name: Through Holes
description:
This game is made for Brackeys Game Jam

And the theme is Hole, so... I came up with holes can portal

The game is still an early prototype, thus there are a lot to improve

Feel free to let me know how you feel playing this game

Any advice or suggestion is welcome!

NOTE:
When you complete the final level, you should see a message! If you don't, it's probably because you didn't get the diamond with landing on the ground It should look like this. Credit: Music / Sweet Jam by kattch Sound Effect / Yay by Higgs01
